Results. We produce a catalogue of 4177 solar-like oscillators, reporting ∆ν and νmax for 98\% of the total star count. The asteroseismic data reveal a vast coverage of the Hertzsprung-Russell diagram, populating the red giant branch, the subgiant regime, and extending towards the main sequence.
