all cases and further confirming the robustness of asteroseismically
determined physical parameters of stars when individual frequencies of
oscillation are available. Baptised as the Kepler dwarfs LEGACY sample,
these stars are the solar-like oscillators with the best asteroseismic
properties available for at least another decade. All data used in this
analysis and the resulting stellar parameters are made publicly
available for the community.},
